            <h2>Take Our Quick Survey &amp; Win a Gift!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear valued customer,</p>
            <p>We appreciate your loyalty and would love to hear about your recent experience with us. To show our appreciation, we're offering a chance to win a [gift] by participating in our quick survey!</p>
