**Notification Email: Update Shipping Details to Claim Your Prize**

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Update Shipping Details to Claim Your Prize</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

       .container {
            width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

       .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }

       .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

       .call-to-action {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

       .call-to-action:hover {
            background-color: #3e8e41;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Update Shipping Details to Claim Your Prize</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear [Recipient's Name],</p>
            <p>We are excited to inform you that you have been selected to receive a special prize from our store. To claim your prize, please update your shipping details by clicking the button below.</p>
            <p>Please note that you must update your shipping details within the next 7 days to receive your prize. If we do not receive your updated shipping details within this time frame, we will be unable to deliver your prize.</p>
            <a href="[Update Shipping Details Link]" class="call-to-action">Update Shipping Details</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

**Email Content**

Subject: Update Shipping Details to Claim Your Prize

Dear [Recipient's Name],

We are excited to inform you that you have been selected to receive a special prize from our store. To claim your prize, please update your shipping details by clicking the button below.

Please note that you must update your shipping details within the next 7 days to receive your prize. If we do not receive your updated shipping details within this time frame, we will be unable to deliver your prize.

[Update Shipping Details Link]

Best regards,
[Your Name]

**How to Use**

1. Replace `[Recipient's Name]` with the actual name of the recipient.
2. Replace `[Update Shipping Details Link]` with the actual link to update the shipping details.
3. Send the email to the recipient using your email service provider.
4. Make sure to include a clear call-to-action button that links to the shipping details update page.

