            <p>As a valued customer, we highly recommend renewing your subscription to ensure continued access to our software and to maintain the security and integrity of your system.</p>
            <p>Expired subscriptions may be vulnerable to security threats and may not receive critical updates and patches, which can lead to data loss and other issues.</p>
            <p>Please click the button below to renew your subscription and continue to enjoy our software's full features and benefits.</p>
            <a href="[Renewal Link]" class="call-to-action">Renew Subscription Now</a>
            <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
